Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(320,435)}Rigel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五车二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(320,435)}Capella
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北河三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(320,435)}Pollux
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参宿四还有    南河三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(256,435)}Betelgeuse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(384,435)}Procyon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狼星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(320,435)}Sirius
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  这什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星太多了拼不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之箭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是迷失方向的话快发现到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就算乱来也要有限制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  我不是有说过无论什么事都说出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服的话你要多少我就借你多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看  小矢来担心得都消瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的是的  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气也变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖气开启了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…终于能够取暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们就来准备吧  正场的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽…虽然刚才是那么说  因为有点混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:22:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  看谁能够一直在户外看星星的比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说看谁能够找到更好的观测地点的比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手对手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底把我的话误会成什么了啦
